<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee2c9b40-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s388a"><num value="388a">§ 388a.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated each fiscal year necessary appropriations to enable the Secretary of Agriculture to carry on the experiments contemplated by <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s388">section 388 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee2c9b41-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1928-04-16/ch377/s3">Apr. 16, 1928, ch. 377, § 3</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/45/431">45 Stat. 431</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
